narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Well, you have to take this class. And you should for the sake of getting to know your peers projects and interests. I just wish it occurred a semester earlier.
Well, if you've gotten this far, you have to take it to graduate. So enjoy your project!
loved learning about fellow classmates art
The class is what you make of it. It's required, but it's really a great chance for you to explore your own work, and (maybe more importantly) the work of your peers.
Be self motivating. Do assignments for yourself every week and take advantage of your advisor and advice from your peers.
